# Ignore everything...
*

# other than specific top-level files...
!.gitignore
!LICENSE
!README.md
!RendScroll.exe

# and top-level source files...
!launcher.py
!index.html

# and Source folders...
!src/
!src/**
!test/
!test/**
!Documentation/
!Documentation/**

# and campaign folders...
!Campaign/
!Campaign/.gitkeep
!images/
!images/.gitkeep
# reusable reference library (Items, …) — committed single source of truth
!Items/
!Items/.gitkeep

# but still ignore compiled Python files
*.pyc
